com.paritytrading.philadelphia

Class FIXConfig.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paritytrading.philadelphia.FIXConfig.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    FIXConfig

    public static class FIXConfig.Builder
extends Object

    A connection configuration builder. The builder uses the following default values:

    • protocol version: FIX 4.2
    • SenderCompID(49): empty
    • TargetCompID(56): empty
    • HeartBtInt(108): 30
    • incoming MsgSeqNum(34): 1
    • outgoing MsgSeqNum(34): 1
    • maximum number of fields in a message: 64
    • field capacity: 64
    • receive buffer capacity: 1024
    • transmit buffer capacity: 1024
    • incoming CheckSum(10) check status: enabled
